title: MONDAY 3/1 - Drew Brees coming back?
itunes:title: MONDAY 3/1 - Drew Brees coming back?
description:
While we speculate on Drew Brees' future, his personal trainer posting a video possibly hinting at a return (0:13). The future of Russell Wilson in Seattle also up in the air. Teammate KJ Wright (1:07) told GMFB he doesn't think Wilson is going anywhere. NFL Network's James Palmer discusses the future of Deshaun Watson in Houston (1:56) while Bucs QB Coach Clyde Christensen (2:46) sees Tom Brady sticking around for quite a while
